---
title: Harissa-Fig Chicken and Golden Halloumi Rice with Garden Greens
description: Smoky harissa and sticky fig spread pair up to drive the flavours of this chicken dinner. Crispy seared halloumi adds extra flavour and protein while golden herbed rice lays the perfect foundation for this trip to flavourtown!
